PN,36501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1776352251
OL,3,C'Midwife dismissed my hallucinations,
OL,4,Cthe next day I was sectioned'
OL,6,FA new mother who was sectioned the day
OL,7,Fafter being classed by a midwife as
OL,8,F"emotionally well" is calling for
OL,9,Fbetter recognition of postpartum
OL,10,Fpsychosis (PP).
OL,12,FLizzy Berryman, from York, said her
OL,13,Fsymptoms were dismissed even after she
OL,14,Fdescribed having hallucinations to a
OL,15,Fhealth professional.
OL,17,FShe was later sedated and then
OL,18,Fsectioned after a psychotic episode.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/17
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1776352251
OL,3,C'Midwife dismissed my hallucinations,
OL,4,Cthe next day I was sectioned'
OL,6,F"It seems that women have to get to
OL,7,Fthe point where they're a danger to
OL,8,Fthemselves or their baby for it to be
OL,9,Fheard," she said.
OL,11,F"You're warned so much about things
OL,12,Flike mastitis, blood clots, but
OL,13,Fthere's just not that much of a
OL,14,Fmention of postpartum psychosis. The
OL,15,Fimpacts can be so devastating."
OL,17,FDespite a healthy pregnancy, Lizzy,
OL,18,F30, started to experience problems
OL,19,Fshortly after giving birth to son
OL,20,FPatrick in 2024.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/17
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1776352251
OL,3,C'Midwife dismissed my hallucinations,
OL,4,Cthe next day I was sectioned'
OL,6,F"On the way home, I told my partner to
OL,7,Fwatch out for runners on the road, but
OL,8,Fthere was no one there," she said.
OL,10,FShe added: "It was about day three and
OL,11,Fmy midwife came to visit me.
OL,13,F"I was laid in bed. I told her, 'I'm
OL,14,Freally confused. I cannot sleep and
OL,15,FI'm hallucinating a little bit' and I
OL,16,Fdidn't know why.
OL,18,F"She ticked that I was emotionally
OL,19,Fwell."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/17
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1776352251
OL,3,C'Midwife dismissed my hallucinations,
OL,4,Cthe next day I was sectioned'
OL,6,FHowever, the following day her "whole
OL,7,Fworld imploded" as she endured a
OL,8,Fpsychotic episode.
OL,10,F"I was screaming for hours, that I was
OL,11,Fin hell, that I'd killed my baby, that
OL,12,FI'd killed my mum," she said.
OL,14,F"I thought I'd killed my entire family
OL,15,Fand that I had died in childbirth. I
OL,16,Feven ran at the window and tried to
OL,17,Fjump out."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/17
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1776352251
OL,3,C'Midwife dismissed my hallucinations,
OL,4,Cthe next day I was sectioned'
OL,6,FShe was taken to York's accident and
OL,7,Femergency department but, after
OL,8,Fsuffering another psychotic episode,
OL,9,Fshe had to be sedated and was
OL,10,Fsectioned.
OL,12,FThe nearest specialist mother and baby
OL,13,Funit (MBU) in Leeds was full. Instead,
OL,14,Fshe was transferred to a facility in
OL,15,FDerby, 90 miles away, to be treated.
OL,17,FNotes she wrote while in Derby showed
OL,18,Fher mental state at the time.
OL,20,FIn one she said: "I'm dying and that
OL,21,Fis okay. Postpartum psychosis is real."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/17
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1776352251
OL,3,C'Midwife dismissed my hallucinations,
OL,4,Cthe next day I was sectioned'
OL,6,FLizzy said: "The care was absolutely
OL,7,Ffantastic. But it was just far - a
OL,8,Flong way from home. It was hard to
OL,9,Fintegrate myself back into real life.
OL,11,F"I think that was the hardest bit
OL,12,Fbecause I felt like I was getting all
OL,13,Fthis specialist care in Derby - that's
OL,14,Fwhere I needed to be.
OL,16,F"When I came back to York, I thought,
OL,17,F'oh my goodness, I'm not going to have
OL,18,Fthat. I'm not going to have the
OL,19,Fpsychiatrist looking after me. I'm not
OL,20,Fgoing to have these daily check-ins'.'"
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/17
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1776352251
OL,3,C'Midwife dismissed my hallucinations,
OL,4,Cthe next day I was sectioned'
OL,6,FLizzy wants to see MBUs become more
OL,7,Fwidely accessible and greater
OL,8,Fawareness of PP among medical
OL,9,Fprofessionals.
OL,11,FShe added: "There have been awful
OL,12,Fstories about women who have gone on
OL,13,Fto do horrible things and, you know,
OL,14,Fharm themselves, harm others.
OL,16,F"And if it was recognised sooner and
OL,17,Fdidn't get to the point where a woman
OL,18,Factually needs to be physically
OL,19,Fsectioned and taken away from their
OL,20,Fbaby and taken away from their family,
OL,21,Fthen I think that would be better."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/17
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1776352251
OL,3,C'Midwife dismissed my hallucinations,
OL,4,Cthe next day I was sectioned'
OL,6,FWhat is postpartum psychosis?
OL,8,FPostpartum psychosis is a serious
OL,9,Fmental illness that can affect anyone
OL,10,Fwithin days or weeks of having a baby.
OL,12,FIt affects around one in 1,000 new
OL,13,Fmothers.
OL,15,FFor some, symptoms can develop
OL,16,Fquickly, while for others they take
OL,17,Flonger to develop. These include
OL,18,Fhallucinations, mania, delusions, low
OL,19,Fmood and feeling confused.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/17
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1776352251
OL,3,C'Midwife dismissed my hallucinations,
OL,4,Cthe next day I was sectioned'
OL,6,FThe condition should be treated as a
OL,7,Fmedical emergency.
OL,9,FFor more information visit Action on
OL,10,FPostpartum Psychosis.
OL,12,FFrankie Roe, from Leeds, said she
OL,13,Fexperienced similar issues following
OL,14,Fthe birth of her first baby, Lexi.
OL,16,FThe now mother-of-two said her
OL,17,Fanxieties were already heightened
OL,18,Fbecause she had previously miscarried.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/17
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1776352251
OL,3,C'Midwife dismissed my hallucinations,
OL,4,Cthe next day I was sectioned'
OL,6,F"I basically spent the entire nine
OL,7,Fmonths of my pregnancy thinking this
OL,8,Fbaby is going to die," she said.
OL,10,F"What probably did go under the radar
OL,11,Fwas the extent to which I was feeling
OL,12,Fanxious about it. That was probably
OL,13,Fwhat was unusual."
OL,15,FShe started antidepressants after
OL,16,Fgiving birth, but experienced "rapid
OL,17,Fmood swings".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/17
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1776352251
OL,3,C'Midwife dismissed my hallucinations,
OL,4,Cthe next day I was sectioned'
OL,6,FShe described being "absolutely manic
OL,7,Fone minute and telling my partner I
OL,8,Ffelt like jumping off a bridge the
OL,9,Fnext".
OL,11,F"My sleep at this point was pretty non-
OL,12,Fexistent and I became convinced that
OL,13,Fit was because of the colour of my bed
OL,14,Fsheets," she said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/17
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1776352251
OL,3,C'Midwife dismissed my hallucinations,
OL,4,Cthe next day I was sectioned'
OL,6,F"I was terrified that I might never
OL,7,Fsleep again and the lack of sleep
OL,8,Fwould kill me. I became increasingly
OL,9,Fpossessive over my baby and refused to
OL,10,Flet my partner take on his share. I
OL,11,Fwas hearing babies crying when I did
OL,12,Fmanage to step away from her for a
OL,13,Fshower or to rest but would come
OL,14,Fdownstairs in a panic to find her
OL,15,Fsleeping peacefully."
OL,17,FAbout 10 weeks after giving birth a
OL,18,Fcrisis team was called, and Frankie
OL,19,Fwas admitted to a MBU.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G12/17
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1776352251
OL,3,C'Midwife dismissed my hallucinations,
OL,4,Cthe next day I was sectioned'
OL,6,FShe said doctors need to get better at
OL,7,Frecognising the symptoms of PP.
OL,9,F"The length of time new GPs spending
OL,10,Fthinking about postpartum psychosis is
OL,11,Fquite minimal compared to depression,"
OL,12,Fshe said.
OL,14,F"It is rare so I understand why that
OL,15,Fmight be the case. But the fact is
OL,16,Fwhen it goes wrong it goes
OL,17,Fdisastrously wrong, the worst case
OL,18,Fscenario is you've got a dead mum and
OL,19,Fa dead baby."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G13/17
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1776352251
OL,3,C'Midwife dismissed my hallucinations,
OL,4,Cthe next day I was sectioned'
OL,6,FThe charity Action on Postpartum
OL,7,FPsychosis supports women and families.
OL,9,FSpokesperson Hannah Bisset said: "Mums
OL,10,Fare still losing their lives, babies
OL,11,Fare still losing their lives, because
OL,12,Fnot everybody knows what postpartum
OL,13,Fpsychosis is and what to do when it
OL,14,Fhappens."
OL,16,FShe added that symptoms can often be
OL,17,Fmisdiagnosed as postnatal depression.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G14/17
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1776352251
OL,3,C'Midwife dismissed my hallucinations,
OL,4,Cthe next day I was sectioned'
OL,6,F"If you're telling someone they've got
OL,7,Fpostnatal depression, whilst it's
OL,8,Fgreat that we all know what that is
OL,9,Fnow, postpartum psychosis is actually
OL,10,Fvery different and requires a much
OL,11,Fmore urgent, speedy response," she
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FA spokesperson for York and
OL,15,FScarborough Teaching Hospitals NHS
OL,16,FFoundation Trust, which treated Lizzy
OL,17,FBerryman, said it was "sorry to hear
OL,18,Fabout Ms Berryman's experience and the
OL,19,Fdistress she and her family have been
OL,20,Fthrough".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G15/17
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36516
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1776352251
OL,3,C'Midwife dismissed my hallucinations,
OL,4,Cthe next day I was sectioned'
OL,6,FThey added: "We take any concerns
OL,7,Fabout the care we provide very
OL,8,Fseriously. While we are unable to
OL,9,Fcomment on individual cases in detail,
OL,10,Fwe would welcome the opportunity to
OL,11,Fspeak directly with Ms Berryman to
OL,12,Fbetter understand her experience and
OL,13,Fensure any learning is identified and
OL,14,Facted upon.
OL,16,F"We are committed to working with our
OL,17,Fpartners to provide safe,
OL,18,Fcompassionate care for all women and
OL,19,Ffamilies, including access to
OL,20,Fspecialist services when needed."
OL,26,@nD@MOUxD@AOU|D@aO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G16/17
